&lt;p&gt;We’re a startup. You’ll be moving fast, context-switching daily, and helping define the culture and process as we go. You’ll have substantial ownership, influence over technical direction, and the opportunity to help build the future of autonomous defense systems from the ground up.&lt;/p&gt;
