&lt;li&gt;Deep expertise in one or more of the following: reinforcement learning, imitation learning, vision-language models, sim-to-real, world modeling, or agentic AI&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience building and evaluating models for embodied agents or autonomous systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in Python and frameworks such as PyTorch, TensorFlow, or JAX&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with large-scale datasets and high-dimensional sensor inputs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to take ideas from research concept to deployed prototype&lt;/li&gt;
